window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Multiverse, the void, existence itself.</b></p> <p>The stakes have never been higher, and it all falls upon the three friends to save the day. Their trip to the Void will prove to be as harmful as lucrative.</p> <p>Their hope? To gain enough power so they can break the Ranking itself.</p> <p>What they haven't thought of is the effect that the absolute and total despair of the Void will have on them. Or even if they will be able to prevail if they ever manage to return.</p> <p><i>This third book of the Physics of the Apocalypse series is a finale that will leave you in tears of sadness and joy.</i></p>"; 
